trans-unit.source: Enumerates the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate" /> objects in an <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" />의 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate" /> 개체를 열거합니다.

trans-unit.source: Enumerators provide read-only access to the data in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 열거자는 컬렉션의에서 데이터에 대 한 읽기 전용 액세스를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Enumerators cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 내부 컬렉션을 수정 하 여 열거자를 사용할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 처음에 열거자는 컬렉션의 첫 번째 요소 앞에 배치됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Reset%2A> method also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Reset%2A> 메서드도 실행 하면 열거자가이 위치로 복원 합니다.

trans-unit.source: At this position, calling the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Current%2A> property throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: 이 위치에서, 호출 된 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Current%2A> 속성 예외를 throw 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 따라서 호출 해야 합니다는 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 하 여 열거자의 값을 읽기 전에 컬렉션의 첫 번째 요소로 메서드 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Current%2A>합니다.

trans-unit.source: This class inherits from the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> interface.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스에서 상속 된 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> 인터페이스입니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about enumerating over a collection, see <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 열거 하는 방법에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" /> to enumerate.
trans-unit.target: 열거할 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator" /> class for the specified <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" />에 대한 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate" />의 현재 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" />를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The current <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator> does not move the position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator> 열거자의 위치를 이동 하지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: Consecutive calls to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Current%2A> property return the same object until either the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Reset%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: 연속 해 서 호출할은 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Current%2A> 될 때까지 동일한 개체를 반환 하는 속성은 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 또는 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Reset%2A> 메서드를 호출 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The enumerator is positioned before the first element of the collection or after the last element.
trans-unit.target: 열거자가 컬렉션의 첫 번째 요소 앞 또는 마지막 요소 뒤에 배치되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 열거자를 컬렉션의 다음 요소로 이동합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <see langword="false" /> if the enumerator has passed the end of the collection.

trans-unit.source: This method advances the enumerator to the next element in the collection.

trans-unit.source: For more information about enumerating over a collection, see the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> topic.

trans-unit.source: Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 첫 번째 요소 앞의 초기 위치에 열거자를 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 열거자는 컬렉션이 변경되지 않은 상태로 유지되는 한 유효한 상태를 유지합니다.

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and the next call to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Reset%2A> method throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션 변경 되 면, 추가 하는 등 요소, 수정 또는 삭제 열거자는 무효화 하 고을 다음에 호출할는 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 또는 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509CertificateCollection.X509CertificateEnumerator.Reset%2A> 메서드가 throw는 <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>합니다.
